r. 2) The application for variation requested that he be allowed to pay any maintenance payable for the said children directly to them. The respondent filed material indicating that the total arrears as of December 2007 were $9,440. 3) The respondent was ordered to pay $380 per month plus 33% of s. expenses. There was nothing in the material filed which would indicate that the mother was not providing support to the children in an appropriate fashion. 4) In the interim, any payments made shall be applied firstly towards the ongoing child support for Keegan and then towards the arrear for Luke."
